                            <comment id="14467915" author="hamletdrc" created="Wed, 30 Sep 2009 21:35:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This was simple to resolve: I went through and audited everywhere ClassNode objects were being created directly through the constructor or ClassHelper factory methods, and looked at the generic information being added. In most cases, I switched the code to use ClassHelper(clazz, false) so that generics are not added to AST nodes by default.  &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
